## Notes:

**For monorepo structure** (Spring Boot and React in same repo):
- Place this `.gitignore` in the root directory
- It covers both backend and frontend

**If you have separate directories:**
```
project-root/
├── backend/          (Spring Boot)
├── frontend/         (React)
└── .gitignore
